#  ‚¢æ‚£æ‚£Ü‚£§‚£§‚£Ñ‚°Ä‚†Ä‚†Ä‚†Ä‚†Ä‚†Ä‚†Ä‚†Ä‚†â‚¢ª‚£ø‚£ø‚£ø‚£ø‚£ø‚£ø‚£ø‚£ø‚£ø‚£ø‚£ø‚£ø‚£ø‚°á                                              
#  ‚†Ä‚†à‚¢ã‚¢π‚†ã‚†â‚†ô‚¢¶‚†Ä‚†Ä‚†Ä‚†Ä‚†Ä‚†Ä‚¢Ä‚£º‚£ø‚£ø‚£ø‚£ø‚£ø‚£ø‚£ø‚£ø‚£ø‚£ø‚£ø‚£ø‚£ø‚°á       Created: 2023/08/05 12:57:51 by oezzaou
#  ‚†Ä‚†Ä‚†Ä‚†ë‚†Ä‚†Ä‚†Ä‚†à‚°á‚†Ä‚†Ä‚†Ä‚†Ä‚£†‚£æ‚£ø‚£ø‚£ø‚£ø‚£ø‚£ø‚£ø‚£ø‚£ø‚£ø‚£ø‚£ø‚£ø‚£ø‚†á       Updated: 2025/02/25 15:19:56 by oezzaou
#  ‚†Ä‚†Ä‚†Ä‚†Ä‚†Ä‚†Ä‚†Ä‚†Ä‚°á‚†Ä‚†Ä‚¢Ä‚£æ‚£ø‚£ø‚†ø‚†ü‚†õ‚†ã‚†õ‚¢ø‚£ø‚£ø‚†ª‚£ø‚£ø‚£ø‚£ø‚°ø‚†Ä                                              
#  ‚†Ä‚†Ä‚†Ä‚†Ä‚†Ä‚†Ä‚†Ä‚¢Ä‚†á‚†Ä‚¢†‚£ø‚£ü‚£≠‚£§‚£∂‚£¶‚£Ñ‚°Ä‚†Ä‚†Ä‚†à‚†ª‚†Ä‚†ò‚£ø‚£ø‚£ø‚†á‚†Ä                                              
#  ‚†Ä‚†Ä‚†Ä‚†Ä‚†Ä‚†±‚†§‚†ä‚†Ä‚¢Ä‚£ø‚°ø‚£ø‚£ø‚£ø‚£ø‚£ø‚£ø‚£ø‚†Ä‚†Ä‚†Ä‚†Ä‚†Ä‚†Ä‚†ò‚£ø‚†è‚†Ä‚†Ä                             ìÜ©‚ôïìÜ™      
#  ‚†Ä‚†Ä‚†Ä‚†Ä‚†Ä‚°Ñ‚†Ä‚†Ä‚†Ä‚†ò‚¢ß‚°Ä‚†Ä‚†Ä‚†∏‚£ø‚£ø‚£ø‚†ü‚†Ä‚†Ä‚†Ä‚†Ä‚†Ä‚†Ä‚†ê‚†ã‚†Ä‚†Ä‚†Ä                     ìÑÇ oussama ezzaouìÜÉ  
#  ‚†Ä‚†Ä‚†Ä‚†Ä‚†Ä‚†ò‚†Ñ‚£Ä‚°Ä‚†∏‚†ì‚†Ä‚†Ä‚†Ä‚††‚†ü‚†ã‚†Å‚†Ä‚†Ä‚†Ä‚†Ä‚†Ä‚†Ä‚†Ä‚†Ä‚†Ä‚†Ä‚†Ä‚†Ä                                              

#====<[ CC compiler: ]>=========================================================
CC						:= c++
CPPFLAGS			:= -Wall -Wextra -Werror -std=c++98
RM						:= rm -rf

#====<[ Colors: ]>==============================================================
GREEN					= \033[1;32m
RED						= \033[1;31m
BLUE					= \033[34m
CYAN					= \033[1;36m
GRAY					= \033[0;90m
PURPLE				= \033[0;35m
YELLOW				= \033[0;93m
BLACK  				= \033[20m
MAGENTA 			= \033[35m
WHITE  				= \033[37m
PINK					= \033[0;38;5;199m
ORANGE 				= \033[38;5;214m
LIGHT_BLACK  	= \033[90m
LIGHT_RED    	= \033[91m
LIGHT_GREEN  	= \033[92m
LIGHT_YELLOW 	= \033[93m
LIGHT_BLUE   	= \033[94m
LIGHT_MAGENTA = \033[95m
LIGHT_CYAN   	= \033[96m
LIGHT_WHITE  	= \033[97m
LIGHT_BLUE		= \033[38;5;45m
RESET					= \033[1;0m

#===<[ Sources: ]>==============================================================
PROJECT				:= M00/ex01
NAME					:= phoneBook 
OBJ_DIR				:= obj
SRC						:= $(wildcard *.cpp)
OBJ						:= $(addprefix $(OBJ_DIR)/, $(addsuffix .o, $(basename $(SRC))))

#====<[ Rules: ]>===============================================================
all: signature $(NAME)

$(NAME): $(OBJ)
	@$(CC) $(CPPFLAGS) $^ -o $@
	@echo "${GREEN}[OK] ${CYAN}$(NAME) ‚úîÔ∏è${RESET}"

$(OBJ_DIR)/%.o: %.cpp | $(OBJ_DIR)
	@$(CC) $(CPPFLAGS) -c $< -o $@
	@printf "$(GREEN)[OK]${RESET} ${PINK}Compiling${RESET} %-26s| $@\n" "$<"

signature:
	@printf "${GRAY}%19s${RESET}\n"	"ìÜ©‚ôïìÜ™"
	@printf "${GRAY}%s${RESET}\n"		"ìÑÇ oussama ezzaouìÜÉ  "

run:
	@./$(NAME)

$(OBJ_DIR):
	@mkdir -p $@

clean:
	@if [ -d $(OBJ_DIR) ]; then\
		${RM} $(OBJ_DIR);\
		printf "${GREEN}[OK]${RESET} ${ORANGE}Cleaning  %-26s${RESET}| ./%s\n"\
					 "... " "$(PROJECT)/$(OBJ_DIR) ‚úîÔ∏è";\
	else\
		printf "${RED}[KO]${RESET} ${BLUE}Not Found %-26s${RESET}| ./%s\n"\
					 "..." "$(PROJECT)/$(OBJ_DIR) ‚úñÔ∏è";\
	fi

fclean: clean
	@if [ -f $(NAME) ]; then\
		${RM} $(NAME);\
		printf "${GREEN}[OK]${RESET} ${ORANGE}Cleaning  %-26s${RESET}| ./%s\n"\
					 "... " "$(PROJECT)/$(NAME) ‚úîÔ∏è";\
	else\
		printf "${RED}[KO]${RESET} ${BLUE}Not Found %-26s${RESET}| ./%s\n"\
					 "..." "$(PROJECT)/$(NAME) ‚úñÔ∏è";\
	fi

re: fclean all

.PHONY: all run clean fclean re signature
#===============================================================================
